user_review: We had the kimchi onion pancakes,  bibimbop, kim bop, and bento box - my favorite were the onion pancakes,  really well made.I have a soft spot for mom and pop Korean family restaurants.

Very nice place with authentic Korean foodmadame owner was very extremely nice and friendly, she replace my meal to a new one and gave me to try other tasty things, i was happy, I had a pleasant  evening!
